{"type":"message","id":"092f2b21","parentId":"f22c6a38","timestamp":"2026-04-10T01:33:38.106Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if the backup is organized with one folder per day. Looking at the repo structure, it's NOT organized by day - it's organized by type (agents/, workspace/, workspace-main/, workspace-selector/, skills/, etc.). Each backup is just a git commit with a date message, not separate dated folders.\n\nThe user expected daily folders. Let me explain the actual structure and offer to change it if they want."},{"type":"text","text":"不是。目前是按**类型分目录**，不是按日期分文件夹：\n\n```\nagents/      ← 所有 agent 数据\nworkspace/   ← 主 workspace\nworkspace-main/\nworkspace-selector/\nskills/\nopenviking/\ncron/\nflows/\nidentity/\n...\n```\n\n每次备份是一个 git commit，commit message 带日期标签（`Full backup 2026-04-10`）。\n\n如果想要**每天一个独立文件夹**（如 `2026-04-10/`、`2026-04-09/`），我可以改成那个结构。要改吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775784810589,"responseId":"0627866ad258784a148424c714af4861"}}
