{"type":"message","id":"3d341589","parentId":"56f5a94e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T01:35:08.004Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants the backup structure changed to daily folders (e.g., `2026-04-10/`, `2026-04-09/`). Let me update the backup script to create a new folder for each day instead of overwriting the same directory structure.\n\nLet me think about the new structure:\n```\nbackup_2026-04-10/\n  agents/\n  workspace/\n  workspace-main/\n  workspace-selector/\n  skills/\n  openviking/\n  ...\nbackup_2026-04-09/\n  agents/\n  ...\n```\n\nBut this means we'd need to clone the whole repo each time and create a new folder, which could get large. Actually, since we push to GitHub, having daily folders means a lot of data duplication.\n \nGit handles this efficiently with compression and delta storage, so daily folders would work fine for a year at around 1MB per day—roughly 365MB total. The user's request for easier rollback makes sense: if something breaks, you can just swap the folder instead of dealing with git commands. Let me modify the script to implement this structure."},{"type":"text","text":"好，改为每天一个独立文件夹。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pbz5rgpdujq0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /tmp/openclaw-full-backup.sh","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775784895032,"responseId":"062786bf40a29eb4104acb8d27281d53"}}
{"type":"message","id":"087bab21","parentId":"3d341589","timestamp":"2026-04-10T01:35:08.126Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pbz5rgpdujq0_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw 全量备份脚本 v2\n# 备份到 GitHub（增量），添加日期标签\n\nset -e\n\nREPO_DIR=\"/tmp/openclaw-backup-git\"\nSOURCE_OPENCLAW=\"$HOME/.openclaw\"\nSOURCE_OPENVIKING=\"$HOME/.openviking\"\nGH_TOKEN=$(grep \"oauth_token:\" ~/.config/gh/hosts.yml | awk '{print $2}')\nREPO=\"https://${GH_TOKEN}@github.com/59330857/openclaw-backup.git\"\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\n\n# 克隆或更新仓库\nif [ -d \"$REPO_DIR/.git\" ]; then\n    cd \"$REPO_DIR\"\n    git pull --quiet origin main\nelse\n    rm -rf \"$REPO_DIR\"\n    git clone --depth 1 \"$REPO\" \"$REPO_DIR\"\n    cd \"$REPO_DIR\"\nfi\n\n# 同步 OpenClaw 配置文件（脱敏）\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='credentials' \\\n    --exclude='logs' \\\n    --exclude='extensions' \\\n    --exclude='subagents' \\\n    --exclude='tasks/runs.sqlite' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/openclaw.json\" ./\n\n# 脱敏 openclaw.json\nif [ -f openclaw.json ]; then\n    python3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('openclaw.json') as f:\n    d = json.load(f)\ndef mask(obj):\n    if isinstance(obj, dict):\n        for k in obj:\n            if k in ('token', 'apiKey', 'password', 'secret', 'socketToken'):\n                obj[k] = '***REDACTED***'\n            else:\n                mask(obj[k])\n    elif isinstance(obj, list):\n        for i in obj:\n            mask(i)\nmask(d)\nwith open('openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(d, f, indent=2)\n\" 2>/dev/null || true\nfi\n\n# 同步 workspace（含记忆、skills、agents、cron、identity）\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='.git' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/workspace/\" \"./workspace/\"\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='.git' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/workspace-main/\" \"./workspace-main/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='.git' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/workspace-selector/\" \"./workspace-selector/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='*.db' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-shm' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-wal' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/agents/\" \"./agents/\"\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/cron/\" \"./cron/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/identity/\" \"./identity/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='*.db' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-shm' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-wal' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/flows/\" \"./flows/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/devices/\" \"./devices/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/delivery-queue/\" \"./delivery-queue/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='memory/lancedb-pro' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/memory/\" \"./memory/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 同步 skills\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='node_modules' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/skills/\" \"./skills/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 同步 OpenViking 关键数据（不含 _system 和 bot）\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='_system' \\\n    --exclude='bot' \\\n    --exclude='.openviking.pid' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENVIKING/\" \"./openviking/\"\n\n# 提交\ngit add -A\nif git diff --cached --quiet; then\n    echo \"[$TODAY] No changes\"\nelse\n    git commit -m \"Full backup $TODAY\"\n    git push --quiet origin main\n    git tag -a \"backup-$TODAY\" -m \"Full backup $TODAY\"\n    git push origin \"backup-$TODAY\" --quiet\n    echo \"[$TODAY] Backup complete\"\nfi"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":65,"aggregated":"#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw 全量备份脚本 v2\n# 备份到 GitHub（增量），添加日期标签\n\nset -e\n\nREPO_DIR=\"/tmp/openclaw-backup-git\"\nSOURCE_OPENCLAW=\"$HOME/.openclaw\"\nSOURCE_OPENVIKING=\"$HOME/.openviking\"\nGH_TOKEN=$(grep \"oauth_token:\" ~/.config/gh/hosts.yml | awk '{print $2}')\nREPO=\"https://${GH_TOKEN}@github.com/59330857/openclaw-backup.git\"\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\n\n# 克隆或更新仓库\nif [ -d \"$REPO_DIR/.git\" ]; then\n    cd \"$REPO_DIR\"\n    git pull --quiet origin main\nelse\n    rm -rf \"$REPO_DIR\"\n    git clone --depth 1 \"$REPO\" \"$REPO_DIR\"\n    cd \"$REPO_DIR\"\nfi\n\n# 同步 OpenClaw 配置文件（脱敏）\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='credentials' \\\n    --exclude='logs' \\\n    --exclude='extensions' \\\n    --exclude='subagents' \\\n    --exclude='tasks/runs.sqlite' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/openclaw.json\" ./\n\n# 脱敏 openclaw.json\nif [ -f openclaw.json ]; then\n    python3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('openclaw.json') as f:\n    d = json.load(f)\ndef mask(obj):\n    if isinstance(obj, dict):\n        for k in obj:\n            if k in ('token', 'apiKey', 'password', 'secret', 'socketToken'):\n                obj[k] = '***REDACTED***'\n            else:\n                mask(obj[k])\n    elif isinstance(obj, list):\n        for i in obj:\n            mask(i)\nmask(d)\nwith open('openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(d, f, indent=2)\n\" 2>/dev/null || true\nfi\n\n# 同步 workspace（含记忆、skills、agents、cron、identity）\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='.git' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/workspace/\" \"./workspace/\"\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='.git' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/workspace-main/\" \"./workspace-main/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='.git' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/workspace-selector/\" \"./workspace-selector/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='*.db' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-shm' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-wal' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/agents/\" \"./agents/\"\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/cron/\" \"./cron/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/identity/\" \"./identity/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='*.db' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-shm' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-wal' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/flows/\" \"./flows/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/devices/\" \"./devices/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/delivery-queue/\" \"./delivery-queue/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='memory/lancedb-pro' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/memory/\" \"./memory/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 同步 skills\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='node_modules' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/skills/\" \"./skills/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 同步 OpenViking 关键数据（不含 _system 和 bot）\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='_system' \\\n    --exclude='bot' \\\n    --exclude='.openviking.pid' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENVIKING/\" \"./openviking/\"\n\n# 提交\ngit add -A\nif git diff --cached --quiet; then\n    echo \"[$TODAY] No changes\"\nelse\n    git commit -m \"Full backup $TODAY\"\n    git push --quiet origin main\n    git tag -a \"backup-$TODAY\" -m \"Full backup $TODAY\"\n    git push origin \"backup-$TODAY\" --quiet\n    echo \"[$TODAY] Backup complete\"\nfi","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775784908109}}
{"type":"message","id":"a138f27e","parentId":"087bab21","timestamp":"2026-04-10T01:35:33.618Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to rewrite the backup script to use daily folders instead of a flat directory structure. Each day gets a folder like `2026-04-10/` containing all the backed-up data.\n\nThe structure should be:\n```\nbackup/\n  2026-04-10/\n    agents/\n    workspace/\n    workspace-main/\n    workspace-selector/\n    skills/\n    openviking/\n    cron/\n    flows/\n    identity/\n    devices/\n    delivery-queue/\n  2026-04-09/\n    ...\n  2026-04-08/\n    ...\n```\n\nThis makes rollback easy - just copy a specific day's folder back to the source location.\n\n\nNow I'm writing a bash script that syncs all the key directories into a dated folder, excluding sensitive files like credentials and logs, then handles the git commit and push for that day's backup."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_envc4koy20yf_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/openclaw-full-backup.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# OpenClaw Daily Folder Backup Script\n# 每天一个独立文件夹，方便回滚\n\nset -e\n\nREPO_DIR=\"/tmp/openclaw-backup-git\"\nSOURCE_OPENCLAW=\"$HOME/.openclaw\"\nSOURCE_OPENVIKING=\"$HOME/.openviking\"\nGH_TOKEN=$(grep \"oauth_token:\" ~/.config/gh/hosts.yml | awk '{print $2}')\nREPO=\"https://${GH_TOKEN}@github.com/59330857/openclaw-backup.git\"\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\nBACKUP_DIR=\"$REPO_DIR/$TODAY\"\n\n# 克隆或更新仓库\nif [ -d \"$REPO_DIR/.git\" ]; then\n    cd \"$REPO_DIR\"\n    git pull --quiet origin main\nelse\n    rm -rf \"$REPO_DIR\"\n    git clone \"$REPO\" \"$REPO_DIR\"\n    cd \"$REPO_DIR\"\nfi\n\n# 创建今日备份目录\nmkdir -p \"$BACKUP_DIR\"\n\n# 同步 OpenClaw 配置（脱敏）\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='credentials' \\\n    --exclude='logs' \\\n    --exclude='extensions' \\\n    --exclude='subagents' \\\n    --exclude='tasks/runs.sqlite' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/openclaw.json\" \"$BACKUP_DIR/openclaw.json.bak\"\n\n# 脱敏 openclaw.json\nif [ -f \"$BACKUP_DIR/openclaw.json.bak\" ]; then\n    python3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('$BACKUP_DIR/openclaw.json.bak') as f:\n    d = json.load(f)\ndef mask(obj):\n    if isinstance(obj, dict):\n        for k in obj:\n            if k in ('token', 'apiKey', 'password', 'secret', 'socketToken'):\n                obj[k] = '***REDACTED***'\n            else:\n                mask(obj[k])\n    elif isinstance(obj, list):\n        for i in obj:\n            mask(i)\nmask(d)\nwith open('$BACKUP_DIR/openclaw.json.bak', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(d, f, indent=2)\n\" 2>/dev/null || true\nfi\n\n# 同步各目录到今日文件夹\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='.git' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/workspace/\" \"$BACKUP_DIR/workspace/\"\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='.git' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/workspace-main/\" \"$BACKUP_DIR/workspace-main/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='.git' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/workspace-selector/\" \"$BACKUP_DIR/workspace-selector/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='*.db' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-shm' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-wal' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/agents/\" \"$BACKUP_DIR/agents/\"\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/cron/\" \"$BACKUP_DIR/cron/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/identity/\" \"$BACKUP_DIR/identity/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='*.db' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-shm' \\\n    --exclude='*.db-wal' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/flows/\" \"$BACKUP_DIR/flows/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/devices/\" \"$BACKUP_DIR/devices/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/delivery-queue/\" \"$BACKUP_DIR/delivery-queue/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 同步 skills\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='node_modules' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENCLAW/skills/\" \"$BACKUP_DIR/skills/\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 同步 OpenViking（不含 _system 和 bot）\nrsync -av --quiet \\\n    --exclude='_system' \\\n    --exclude='bot' \\\n    --exclude='.openviking.pid' \\\n    \"$SOURCE_OPENVIKING/\" \"$BACKUP_DIR/openviking/\"\n\n# 提交\ncd \"$REPO_DIR\"\ngit add -A\nif git diff --cached --quiet; then\n    echo \"[$TODAY] No changes\"\nelse\n    git commit -m \"Full backup $TODAY\"\n    git push --quiet origin main\n    git tag -a \"backup-$TODAY\" -m \"Full backup $TODAY\"\n    git push origin \"backup-$TODAY\" --quiet\n    echo \"[$TODAY] Backup complete\"\nfi\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775784908129,"responseId":"062786cc051ad5f2963bfe6d774e5ebc"}}
